Package: betScrapeR
Title: R package to scrape live sports betting odds
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Sheehan", email = "davidfsheehan87@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R package that combines exchange data from the Betfair API with web scraped odds from various bookmakers. This information can then inform and improve trading strategies.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dashee87/betScrapeR
BugReports: http://www.github.com/dashee87/betScrapeR/issues
Maintainer: David Sheehan <davidfsheehan87@gmail.com>
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rvest (>= 0.3.0),
    DT (>= 0.1.0),
    shinydashboard
Suggests:
